                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43693016/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2017-05-07 14:32
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="43669322">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63956076/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u63956076-11.jpg" alt="猫薄荷" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43669322/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43669322/" class="">第203页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63956076/" class=" " title="猫薄荷">猫薄荷</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43669322">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们习惯性地认为，不可设想的行为只有在人停止思考时才可能发生：即从前社会的、蒙昧的人类情感的大锅之上揭开理性之盖的时候。 人们引以为豪的理性，脱离了道德的限制，便成了恶魔的帮手。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-06 14:21</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote>我们习惯性地认为，不可设想的行为只有在人停止思考时才可能发生：即从前社会的、蒙昧的人类情感的大锅之上揭开理性之盖的时候。</blockquote><p>人们引以为豪的理性，脱离了道德的限制，便成了恶魔的帮手。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
